race.comment: Tough race. ODINAKA (10) is a super consistent galloper who was a winner three back then placed last two. Less weight here and deserves another win. LITTLE SILVER (9) was fifth behind EXCELTRAIN last time. Tricky gate and expected to roll forward and can give a sight. PROPHET AND POWER (2) wasn't disgraced fresh over 1400m off a long break. Has good speed and should feature over the mile. OTHERONESON (7) has been mixing form and it's been an age since a win but did score only try this course and distance. Could be overs. ROCKING SOCIETY (3) resumes. Ultra consistent and expecting more of the same.
